community/batteries/blob/af731107d531b39cd7278c73f91c573f40340612/Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.lean#L294-L303","name":"Batteries.Vector.eraseIdxN","line":294,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.html#Batteries.Vector.eraseIdxN","doc":"`eraseIdxN v i h` removes the element at position `i` from a vector of length `n`.\n`h : i < n` has a default argument `by get_elem_tactic` which tries to supply a proof\nthat the index is valid.\n\nThis function takes worst case O(n) time because it has to backshift all elements at positions\ngreater than i.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.html#Batteries.Vector.eraseIdxN\"><span class=\"name\">Batteries</span>.<span class=\"name\">Vector</span>.<span class=\"name\">eraseIdxN</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{n : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(v : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.html#Batteries.Vector\">Batteries.Vector</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(i : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(h : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">i</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LT.lt\">&lt;</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span> := by get_elem_tactic)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.html#Batteries.Vector\">Batteries.Vector</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSub.hSub\">-</a> <span class=\"fn\">1</span>)</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/af731107d531b39cd7278c73f91c573f40340612/Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.lean#L283-L292","name":"Batteries.Vector.eraseIdx!","line":283,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.html#Batteries.Vector.eraseIdx!","doc":"`O(|v| - i)`. `eraseIdx! v i` removes the element at position `i` from vector `v` of length `n`.\nPanics if `i` is not less than `n`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.html#Batteries.Vector.eraseIdx!\"><span class=\"name\">Batteries</span>.<span class=\"name\">Vector</span>.<span class=\"name\">eraseIdx!</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{n : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(v : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.html#Batteries.Vector\">Batteries.Vector</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(i : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.html#Batteries.Vector\">Batteries.Vector</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSub.hSub\">-</a> <span class=\"fn\">1</span>)</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/af731107d531b39cd7278c73f91c573f40340612/Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.lean#L277-L281","name":"Batteries.Vector.tail","line":277,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.html#Batteries.Vector.tail","doc":"`Vector.tail` produces the tail of the vector `v`. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.html#Batteries.Vector.tail\"><span class=\"name\">Batteries</span>.<span class=\"name\">Vector</span>.<span class=\"name\">tail</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{n : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(v : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.html#Batteries.Vector\">Batteries.Vector</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.html#Batteries.Vector\">Batteries.Vector</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSub.hSub\">-</a> <span class=\"fn\">1</span>)</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/af731107d531b39cd7278c73f91c573f40340612/Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.lean#L273-L275","name":"Batteries.Vector.feraseIdx","line":273,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.html#Batteries.Vector.feraseIdx","doc":"`O(|v| - i)`. `feraseIdx v i` removes the element at position `i` in vector `v`. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/Vector/Basic.html#Batteries.Vector.feraseIdx\"><span class=\"name\">Batteries</span>.<s